</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#Attribute"><span class="toc-number">1.3.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">Attribute</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-JavaScript-%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%BC%8F"><span class="toc-number">1.3.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">使用 JavaScript 表达式</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0"><span class="toc-number">1.3.5.</span> <span class="toc-text">参数</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0"><span class="toc-number">1.3.6.</span> <span class="toc-text">动态参数</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%AF%B9%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%80%BC%E7%9A%84%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%9F"><span class="toc-number">1.3.6.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">对动态参数的值的约束</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%AF%B9%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%9F"><span class="toc-number">1.3.6.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">对动态参数表达式的约束</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E4%BF%AE%E9%A5%B0%E7%AC%A6"><span class="toc-number">1.3.7.</span> <span class="toc-text">修饰符</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%EF%BC%88%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5%E5%93%8D%E5%BA%94%E5%BC%8F%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%EF%BC%89"><span class="toc-number">1.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">数据代理（深入响应式原理）</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-1"><a class="toc-link" href="#Vue3%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%8B"><span class="toc-number">2.</span> <span class="toc-text">Vue3快速上手</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#1-Vue3%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B"><span 